Ana sa ran ruwan sama mai inci 2 zuwa 4 a wasu sassan yankin, musamman a yankin Arizona.
Ruwa mai sauri yana yiwuwa a yanayin da ke saurin lalacewa saboda yanayin ruwan sama na tropical.
Ba zai dace ba mutum ya yi tafiya a cikin hamada don ya fuskanci barazanar ruwan sama mai zafi.
