Taron Trump a West Virginia, Tashar Youtube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara wani taron zanga-zangar dare a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan ne zanga-zangar farko da Trump ya yi a cikin mako guda, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da aka dakatar da amincewar da aka yi masa na zabensa na cike da wani wuri a Kotun Koli, Trump na neman gina goyon baya ga zaben na rabin lokaci mai zuwa saboda 'yan Republican na cikin hadarin rasa ikon majalisar dokokin kasar a lokacin da aka kada kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi zanga-zangar Trump a West Virginia da daddare kuma yaya za ku ga ta a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia an shirya shi ne don 7 pm ET yau, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon zanga-zangar Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump na iya jawabi a wannan makon domin zaben kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya karu saboda zargin lalata da aka yi da kuma an dakatar da amincewar Majalisar Dattijai har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban manufar wannan zanga-zangar ita ce taimaka wa 'yan Republican su fuskanci zaben watan Nuwamba don samun karfafawa.
Saboda haka, yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce wadannan zanga-zangar biyar na mako mai zuwa suna nufin samar da makamashi ga masu sa kai da magoya bayan su yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjayen da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Shugaban kasa yana da matukar muhimmanci ga wannan shiri cewa shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama a lokacin da muke shirin shiga cikin yakin neman zabe", wani mai magana da yawun Trump ya shaida wa Reuters wanda ya ƙi ambaci sunansa.
An shirya a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, za a iya samun magoya bayan taron daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a iya samun labarin Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne za a yi ziyarar Trump ta biyu a watan da ya gabata a West Virginia, jihar da ta samu sama da maki 40 a shekarar 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Jam'iyyar Republican ta West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ya rasa a cikin binciken.
"Ba shi da kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo don ya yi ƙoƙari ya ba shi damar yin bincike", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
