A lokacin da yake magana da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce ya yi imanin cewa wani abu ya tafi daidai ba kuma yana da shakku game da yadda za a magance matsalar toxic masculinity a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri 'yar wasan kwaikwayo ta Game of Thrones Rose Leslie, mai shekara 31, ya yarda cewa yana da sha'awa sosai wajen magance batun.
Na ji ina da sha'awa sosai, a yanzu - ina muka yi kuskure da namiji?, ya ce.
