Domin shi ne quite a fili cewa wani abu ya tafi ba daidai ba ga jariri.
A cikin hira ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi prequels ko sequels na Game of Thrones ba lokacin da jerin suka ƙare a lokacin rani mai zuwa, yana cewa wannan shine yaƙi da dawakai.
Daga watan Nuwamba Kit zai bayyana a sabon samar da Sam Shepard na True West wanda shine labarin mai samar da fina-finai da ɗan'uwansa, wanda ya bar shi.
A kwanan nan, actor ya bayyana cewa yana ganin cewa haduwa da matarsa Rose ita ce mafi kyawun abu da ya fito daga Game of Thrones.
"Na sadu da matata a wannan shirin, don haka wannan shine yadda zan sami iyalina na gaba, da rayuwata daga nan gaba", in ji shi.
