HIV/Aids: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar 14% a cikin sabbin shari'o'i
Kasar Sin ta ba da sanarwar tashi da kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan 'yan kasar da ke rayuwa da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar, in ji jami'an lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kawai an ruwaito wasu sabbin mutane 40,000.
Mafi yawan sabbin cututtuka sun kasance na jima'i, wanda ke nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin sakamakon karuwar jini mai cutar.
Amma yawan mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar an rage ta zuwa kusan sifili, jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun ce a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
