Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya mai wakilci da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da shi.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don taron (har sai kun kasance a shirye ku biya tikitin VIP), masu halartar taron suna da su kammala jerin ayyuka, ko ayyuka kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa ga shugabannin duniya, yin waya ko wasu hanyoyi masu muhimmanci na taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burinsu na kawar da talauci.
