Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, a ranar Laraba, ya yi magana game da ƙarin kuɗin da aka biya na China Daily a cikin Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan ya zargi China da neman shiga cikin zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na 6 ga Nuwamba, yana zargin cewa China ta ƙi.
