Mai kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin kaddamar da wani sabon intanet don yin gasa da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, zai kaddamar da wani sabon kasuwanci da zai yi gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne wanda ke gina kan dandamali na tushen tushen tushen Solid na Berners-Lee.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda ake adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanda mutane ke da izinin samun damar wane bayani.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya bayyana cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce mamaye duniya.
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", ya ce game da sabon kasuwanci.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don ba mutane damar ƙirƙirar shagon yanar gizo na bayanan sirri ko POD.
Wannan zai iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalandar, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da sauran kayan aiki na mutum da na sana'a.
Wannan yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna samuwa a kan mai bincike guda ɗaya kuma duk a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke sa shagon yanar gizo na bayanan sirri ya zama na musamman shi ne cewa yana cikin ikon mai amfani ne ya samu damar yin amfani da irin bayanan da ake samu.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "kawo kanka cikin sirri ta hanyar bayanai.
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, ita ce kamfanin ya kawo albarkatu, ƙwarewar tsari da kuma ƙwarewar da ta dace don yin Solid samuwa ga kowa.
A halin yanzu kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta kawo, wasu masu haɓaka a cikin ma'aikatan da ke da kwangila don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu coders masu son rai.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu bunkasa fasaha a duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen su na rarraba ta hanyar kayan aikin da ke samuwa a shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da Facebook da Google game da ko za su gabatar da cikakken canji inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su zai koma sama daga kasa daga yau zuwa gobe.
Ba mu nemi izinin su ba.
A wani shafin yanar gizo da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa, manufa ta Inrupt ita ce samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu da zai taimaka wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon shafin da aka gina a Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sake fasalin Intanet lokacin da ya kafa Ƙungiyar World Wide Web a Cibiyar Fasaha a Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da yake yana fara Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance Founder da kuma Daraktan Consortium na World Wide Web, Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
"Ina da tabbaci sosai game da wannan zamani na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
