Shugaban majalisar dattijai Nancy Pelosi ta kira dan takarar kotun koli Mr Brett Kavanaugh mai cike da damuwa kuma ta ce ba zai iya aiki a kotun koli ba saboda halayensa na zamani.
Pelosi ta yi wannan bayanin a wata hira da ta yi a ranar Asabar a Texas Tribune Festival a Austin, Texas.
"Ba zan iya yin tunani ba game da gaskiyar cewa idan wata mace ta taɓa yin hakan, za a ce ta kasance mai ban mamaki", in ji Pelosi game da yadda ta amsa shaidar Kavanaugh a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai a ranar Alhamis.
