Turai ta yi murnar lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Team Europe ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup 2018 a kan Team USA da ƙimar ƙarshe ta 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a waje da Paris, Faransa.
Yanzu Amurka ta yi asara sau shida a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kofin lokacin da tawagar dan Denmark Thomas Bjorn ta kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata don ta doke Amurka.
Phil Mickelson wanda ya fi kowa a Amurka, wanda ya yi fama da rashin ƙarfi a duk lokacin gasar, ya buga shi a cikin ruwa a rami 16 na par-3, don haka ya mika wasansa ga Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiyanci Molinari ya fita a duk zagaye, kuma ya zama 1 daga cikin 'yan wasa 4 da suka taba samun 5-0-0 tun lokacin da tsarin gasar ta yanzu ya fara a 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya yi rashin nasara 5&4 a kan dan wasan da ya fi kowa a tawagar Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, dan wasan duniya mafi girma, ya kawo 2 da 1 ga Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda ya buga wasan Ryder Cup na karshe.
Tsohon dan wasan Ryder Cup guda takwas, Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama dan wasan Turai mafi kyau a gasar ta kasance tare da maki 25.5 a cikin aikinsa.
